snippet.title: Greyhill Incident - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Greyhill Incident releases on june 9th 2023 and will be available on Steam, Playstation 4, 5 and XBOX X, S.

Wishlist it Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1905020/Greyhill_Incident/

Greyhill Incident is a story-driven Survival-Horror game about an classic Alien-Invasion takes place during the early 90s. As Ryan Baker, equipped with a baseball bat and a few bullets in his revolver, the story takes you across the atmospheric neighborhood of Greyhill which is invaded by UFOs & Grey Aliens.
